snippet.title: DYEING my BROWN hair BLUE with MANIC PANIC *NO BLEACH* tutorial | her habits vlog
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome back to the her habits channel! In this vlog, I attempt to attain a Billie Eilish look by dying my brown hair blue with Manic Panic "After Midnight" semi-permanent hair dye! No bleach was involved in the making of this video. If your hair is light enough, Manic Panic hair dye can be a great option if you are worried about damaging your hair. Hope you enjoy this dying hair blue "tutorial" vlog. 

follow me on instagram: @herhabitschannel 👉https://www.instagram.com/herhabitschannel/

LATEST ORIGINAL SONG: https://youtu.be/-EoF4OcmXdY
